{"tid":1434847,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"五四、六九，剛巧隔了一百年。香港人在創造歷史","createTime":"2019-08-09T01:40:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T01:48:56.000Z","uid":278839,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d411120b42ac5a0bdcbad5f7552a3a56c3ba627d","tid":1434847,"uid":278839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:40:00.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">1919年5月</span></strong>，北京民眾上街抗議國民政府無能，割讓山東省利益，喪權辱國，未能守護好國民利益。當時的口號是<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「外爭國權，內除國賊」</span></span></strong>，並火燒出賣山東國族權益的曹汝霖官邸。其他城市之後也舉行了類似的抗議遊行，社會各界的成員也加入。抗議活動的高潮是當年6月的大罷工，它使當時中國的主要工業中心及港口上海陷入癱瘓。<br />\n<br />\n共產黨創黨人陳獨秀，當年1月在《&quot;新青年&quot;罪案之答辯書》中提出要擁護德先生（民主）和賽先生（科學)，並且認為：「我們現在認定這兩位先生，可以救治中國政治上、道德上、學術上、思想上一切的黑暗。」<br />\n<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">2019年6月</span></strong>，香港民眾上街抗議香港政府無能，割讓一國兩制下的兩制利益，強推送中條例，斷送香港人的自由和國際金融中心的地位。當時的口號是<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「光復香港，時代革命」</span></span></strong>&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n未完。待續。"},{"pid":"9182731940176ed88a1e73eafc19ac2a4e93292a","tid":1434847,"uid":278839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:40:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9067dd02531f1e8876520a18eb8d6282ecc822a4","tid":1434847,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:41:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4kTJ9uU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4kTJ9uU.jpg&h=3670e858&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f8780abb10c58a07d0c65cfb76333fba5c908375","tid":1434847,"uid":4618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote